metadata.name: First love garnet ring
metadata.description:
A broken heart is an expression of a meaningful feeling and great emotion in life. For many people it is their first love experience.

Often the first love changes everything: your attitude, expectations, goals from relationships, life, this change needs to be remembered as a starting point for a new life.

Material: This ring is made from garnet. Garnets are known as powerful gemstones for love and relationships, able to assist you in drawing more love into your life for yourself and others.
